Class IgnoredFile

Namespace
MdFilesMerger.Domain.Entity
Assembly
MdFilesMerger.Domain.dll

Implementation of ignored file model associated with .md file located in main directory, whose content won't be included in created merged file.

Inheritance: BaseItem -> BaseDirectory -> MdFile -> RelativeFile -> IgnoredFile
Implements: IComparable<T>, IDirectory, IIgnoredFile, IItem, IRelativeFile 

public sealed class IgnoredFile : RelativeFile, IIgnoredFile, IRelativeFile, IDirectory, IItem, IComparable<IDirectory>

Parameters

id int

The item identification number.

path string

Valid relative path to existing .md file associated with this item. Path should use '/' as directory separator.

mainDirId int

Id of MainDirectory object associated with this item.

modifiedDate DateTime

Date and time of last modification of this entity.

Remarks

No evaluation or adjusting is performed, so use this method only for already evaluated and prepared data, for example from database.
